"We will lose everything", a 2016 report by the Diocese of Brisbane, contains evidence of atrocities committed in the previous year, such as extrajudicial killings, torture, particularly frequent, as claimed by another report, rape and electrocution, and the brutal suppression of peaceful demonstrations.
